The '''Finland national under-17 football team''' represents [[Finland]] in international [[football (soccer)|football]] competitions in the [[FIFA U-17 World Cup]] and the [[UEFA European Under-17 Football Championship]], as well as any other under-17 international football tournaments. It is governed by the [[Football Association of Finland]].

==Current squad==
The following players were called for the [[2012 UEFA European Under-17 Football Championship qualifying round]] matches on 24-29 October 2011.<ref>[http://www.palloliitto.fi/viestinta/?num=195914 U17: Joukkue EM-karsintaan]</ref>
